{"tid":1132596,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AKB48劇場入座率低 成員性感演出吸客","createTime":"2019-04-30T12:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T12:39:37.000Z","uid":50980,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"799e10392dccd1324c615d6ba80641d0159835fa","tid":1132596,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/news/20190430/1556563288504/akb48%e5%8a%87%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%a5%e5%ba%a7%e7%8e%87%e4%bd%8e-%e6%88%90%e5%93%a1%e6%80%a7%e6%84%9f%e6%bc%94%e5%87%ba%e5%90%b8%e5%ae%a2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Fnews%2F20190430%2F1556563288504%2Fakb48%25e5%258a%2587%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%25ba%25a7%25e7%258e%2587%25e4%25bd%258e-%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%2580%25a7%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%25bc%2594%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2590%25b8%25e5%25ae%25a2&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1frdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=6598b1ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Fnews%2F20190430%2F1556563288504%2Fakb48%25e5%258a%2587%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%25ba%25a7%25e7%258e%2587%25e4%25bd%258e-%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%2580%25a7%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%25bc%2594%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2590%25b8%25e5%25ae%25a2&h=154b7dcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/news/20190430/1556563288504/akb48%e5%8a%87%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%a5%e5%ba%a7%e7%8e%87%e4%bd%8e-%e6%88%90%e5%93%a1%e6%80%a7%e6%84%9f%e6%bc%94%e5%87%ba%e5%90%b8%e5%ae%a2</a><br />\n<br />\n明報專訊】日本女團AKB48自2005年出道以來，唱片銷量多次創下佳績，憑着隊中多名人氣成員，AKB48一直穩守日本樂壇最紅女團地位。不過乃木坂46、櫸坂46等近年相繼堀起，AKB48的人氣成員又逐一離隊，包括前日剛完成畢業演唱會的「一姐」指原莉乃，導致AKB48聲勢大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n最新一期日本雜誌《週刊實話》報道，幾乎每天都有AKB48成員演出的AKB48劇場，近年因欠缺主將助陣，導致入座率下滑。消息人士指劇場為了挽救票房，本月中開始安排成員性感演出，不但穿上如內衣的造型登場，在台上更有不少躺臥動作，有忠實粉絲看罷大表驚訝，慨嘆「AKB要沒落了」；不過亦有粉絲讚成員造型新潮。<br />\n<br />\n提起指原莉乃，日前舉行畢業演出的她，完騷後受訪不忘談及姊妹團NGT48成員山口真帆遇襲事件，指原莉乃稱，與其說公司有改善空間，不如說應該從頭做起，「我覺得不是一個人能夠改變得到」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190430/s00008/2802f33fff3b6f7ed993b73df88e0ba7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190430%2Fs00008%2F2802f33fff3b6f7ed993b73df88e0ba7.jpg&h=bea290c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f887d5aa5e111eb1cfe77c0ecb8df5e9c2d3c70","tid":1132596,"uid":54931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:05:21.000Z","msg":"無可能架 日本係賣青春 唔會賣肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定係死韓狗搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe30d47d46bc0bea60c80873c43091b9ee5b32d","tid":1132596,"uid":45178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"屌佢次次去日本抽足5日都抽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超級遠方又冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇AKB變番SDN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係NGZ好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d93b69e54567b826327d52bdf87128cd67009c","tid":1132596,"uid":24521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"快啲接埋佢啦 <br />\n咪再做衰個名 雖然已經好臭"},{"pid":"8d8d83efb4e6d7727761c270b7f8c598585e6161","tid":1132596,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"搞感謝祭啦"}]}